    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a recently overhauled double-VANOS system and reinforced rod bearings, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are track-ready. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced with plates to mitigate floor fatigue. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and chassis rigidity remain the focal points of this driver-spec icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
