      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride and it's looking for a brand new home. It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really great shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car for daily commutes or fun weekend trips. It runs super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it! If you're looking for a solid, honest vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, come take it for a spin and see if it's the right fit for you!",
