    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with updated bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system refresh. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is dialed and ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duty.",
